org.apache.hadoop.hive.common.type

Class Timestamp

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.common.type.Timestamp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Timestamp>

    public class Timestamp
extends Object
implements Comparable<Timestamp>
    This is the internal type for Timestamp. The full qualified input format of Timestamp is "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss[.SSS...]", where the time part is optional. If time part is absent, a default '00:00:00.0' will be used.
